{"tid":1221043,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[每日一犬] 每日重點關愛新犬隻","createTime":"2019-06-14T06:27:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T06:45:22.000Z","uid":71004,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"783c00cb7cce684eb721ad97358fde2b28cfafc3","tid":1221043,"uid":71004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T06:27:50.000Z","msg":"狗係人類最好嘅朋友 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見到近日巴打們傾囊分享咗唔少佢地認識嘅狗 頓時發覺連登有愛 原來大家都鍾意狗狗 特別係黑犬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n作為動物愛好者嘅我當然係想藉此機會深入認識新狗狗 俾佢地知道人類對佢地嘅關懷<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係我覺得單單收集狗狗資料係唔夠嘅, 因為呢d 唔夠針對性嘅行動 <br />\n好容易做成錯覺 令呢班狗狗以為大家知完就算 唔會將心中愛嘅實踐 從而感到備受冷落<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以啊 我覺得要發起<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">每日一犬</span></strong> 每日介紹一隻狗狗作為重點關愛對象<br />\n集結連登仔嘅力量 話俾佢地知人間有愛 做狗路上永不孤單 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最重要係教識佢地一個道理<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">善惡到頭終有報 只爭來早與來遲</span></strong> <br />\n<br />\n警員 廖軒俊 廖軒逸<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1220587/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1220587/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n請問大家支唔支持<br />\n支持請 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反對請 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce7144d43b34fee01927b7c42aae5d2c5ac9e154","tid":1221043,"uid":71004,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T06:35:47.000Z","msg":"小心打擾到警察叔叔<br />\n<br />\n原來指使訓練畜龍同黑警變成獸兵嘅，就係呢兩條鬼佬！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1219611/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1219611/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n[突發] 毅進警犬 身份資料+老竇老母曝光<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1220419/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1220419/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n（有圖）有女警比人起咗底！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1217455/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1217455/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n杜 家 樂 警 員 - 中華傳道會劉永生中學第一屆DSE畢業<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1219868/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1219868/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"3a48721831ec9e51730b820b31f23beb4c0167a6","tid":1221043,"uid":67896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T06:45:22.000Z","msg":"推啊"}]}